11:T55d,I didn’t like this so much as last year’s “Million Dollar Pentagram” as the child-sized super sleuth has to get to grips with a mystery set amidst the snowy Yatsugatake mountains. A gunshot, an avalanche and an assault on a member of staff at the local astronomical telescope soon has police inspector “Kansuke” - himself a survivor of that perilous snowfall, only now with just the one functioning eye - at the scene of the crime trying to piece together just what is going on in this desolate and pristine wilderness. All the while, the ever-observant “Conan” is collecting clues, deducing and deliberating from a diminutive position that allows him unfettered access to the scene. As the investigation gathers pace, there seem to be more and more police and government agencies to contend with so a conspiracy is clearly rife! For me, there simply isn’t enough “Conan” in this animation; there are too many characters for us to follow and the story itself is a little too convoluted, especially at an ending that’s excitingly animated by a bit underwhelming. It’s also probably half an hour too long to sustain the pace that I found a bit lacklustre all too often. Next time, maybe less focus on the already super-served thwhack and pow combat elements and more emphasis on the detective elements for our intrepid sleuth facing a strong baddie.5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Movie\",\"name\":\"Detective Conan: One-Eyed Flashback\",\"description\":\"As police inspector Yamato Kansuke pursues a certain man in the snowy mountains of Nagano, a shadow suddenly appears in his field of vision. While he's distracted, a rifle bullet fired by someone grazes his left eye and causes an avalanche accompanied by a roar. Ten months later, Kansuke, having miraculously survived the avalanche, receives a report that a researcher at the Nobeyama National Astronomical Observatory has been attacked.\",\"image\":\"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1wl6eAHbIDSz61tGwYTOKlSRvZb.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2025-04-18\",\"numberOfEpisodes\":null,\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"inLanguage\":\"ja\",\"genre\":[\"Animation\",\"Action\",\"Mystery\",\"Crime\"],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":7.4,\"bestRating\":10,\"ratingCount\":47}}"}}],["$","$L10",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"4ee28a69-0a54-46ed-83ba-7d1a5805d995","tmdb_id":1396965,"imdb_id":"tt35444710","content_type":"movie","title":"Detective Conan: One-Eyed Flashback","original_title":"名探偵コナン 隻眼の残像","overview":"As police inspector Yamato Kansuke pursues a certain man in the snowy mountains of Nagano, a shadow suddenly appears in his field of vision. While he's distracted, a rifle bullet fired by someone grazes his left eye and causes an avalanche accompanied by a roar. Ten months later, Kansuke, having miraculously survived the avalanche, receives a report that a researcher at the Nobeyama National Astronomical Observatory has been attacked.","poster_path":"/1wl6eAHbIDSz61tGwYTOKlSRvZb.jpg","backdrop_path":"/zjKsqMASzGLh21C2GT1fuaa9mDP.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-18","first_air_date":null,"status":"published","original_language":"ja","origin_country":["JP"],"genres":[{"id":16,"name":"Animation"},{"id":28,"name":"Action"},{"id":9648,"name":"Mystery"},{"id":80,"name":"Crime"}],"popularity":4.4795,"vote_average":7.4,"vote_count":47,"runtime":109,"number_of_seasons":null,"number_of_episodes":null,"created_at":"2026-02-25T22:53:43.245303+00:00","updated_at":"2026-02-25T22:53:43.036+00:00","tagline":"The once sleeping case is now awake ⎯","homepage":null,"budget":0,"revenue":166061012,"production_companies":[{"id":882,"name":"TOHO","logo_path":"/fRSWWjquvzcHjACbtF53utZFIll.png","origin_country":"JP"},{"id":7164,"name":"TMS Entertainment","logo_path":"/vHsaqTkQ2ZTbdqrCA272YahoVlg.png","origin_country":"JP"},{"id":9149,"name":"Shogakukan","logo_path":"/isLUpud9N56ifftJZ4XvzwBBpoG.png","origi