"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0},{"width":720,"height":1080,"file_path":"/cShSrMVsjv5Y81JBUghyhz8AnqA.jpg","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0},{"width":1926,"height":2890,"file_path":"/zBXBDguzU9kEVgqob2VTeA5LZwi.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.666,"vote_average":0},{"width":1440,"height":2030,"file_path":"/mriHyCnEU2Zh793ePdPcKcDFnyl.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.709,"vote_average":0},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/siD5zq5dz4WVQJZyDEhkOEkkOgy.jpg","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":2121,"height":1193,"file_path":"/zjKsqMASzGLh21C2GT1fuaa9mDP.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":5,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":8.034},{"width":1931,"height":1086,"file_path":"/bE10DMcePbEWa8LAWZQ16vQNrwT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1931,"height":1086,"file_path":"/12U6uJLYE0ZsBjcKmhXHLoMUAJw.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/4o9tOb9ToINF1PeoymQ8iAVtRsT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/vlmr51NGFdbtBpP5ByMminu9aIn.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":2133,"height":1200,"file_path":"/4QEwYMnfZf2LYrN5w9W4h8uAwty.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":2840,"height":1598,"file_path":"/wWZlrv04xeQ1P2sYGpFtbKMM3W2.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":1.75}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-26T03:31:57.957+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"名侦探柯南：独眼的残像","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"长野县八岳连峰未宝岳。长野县警大和敢助在雪山上追赶“某个男人”时，突然有什么人的影子出现在了敢助的视野中。回过神来的瞬间，“某个男人”射出的步枪子弹掠过了敢助的左眼，伴随着地面轰鸣发生了雪崩。敢助就这样被吞噬——  10个月后。接到野边山国立天文台的设施研究员被某人袭击的报警后，从雪崩中奇迹般生还的敢助，和上原由衣赶到了现场。正在了解情况的时候天文台的巨大抛物面天线启动了，敢助受伤了的左眼不知为何突然剧烈地疼痛起来……  那天晚上，毛利侦探事务所接到了小五郎警视厅时期关系很好的同事、被称作“鳄鱼”的刑警的电话。他正在未宝岳调查将敢助卷入的雪崩事故，据说案件文档中有小五郎的名字。  柯南也跟着约定和“鳄鱼”日后见面的小五郎同去，但在前往约好的地点的途中，突然响起了枪声。  没有实现的约定，与存在于独眼中的残像。  在冰雪肆虐的山岳之上，白茫茫的因缘（乳白天空谜案）之帷幕被拉开了——"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":110,"tagline":"眠っていた記憶が、目を覚ます──","homepage":"https://www.conan-movie.jp/2025/","overview":"長野県・八ヶ岳連峰未宝岳。長野県警の大和敢助が雪山で“ある男”を追っていた時、不意に何者かの影が敢助の視界に。気をとられた瞬間、“ある男”が放ったライフル弾が敢助の左眼をかすめ、大きな地響きとともに雪崩が発生。そのまま敢助を飲み込んでしまい―  10 カ月後。国立天文台野辺山の施設研究員が何者かに襲われたという通報を受け、雪崩から奇跡的に生還した敢助と、上原由衣が現場へ駆けつけた。事情聴取のさなか天文台の巨大パラボラアンテナが動き出すと、 負傷し隻眼となった敢助の左眼がなぜか突如激しく疼きだす…  その夜、毛利探偵事務所に、小五郎の警視庁時代に仲の良い同僚だった“ワニ”と呼ばれる刑事から電話が入った。未宝岳で敢助が巻き込まれた雪崩事故を調査しており、事件ファイルに小五郎の名前があったという。後日会う約束を交わした小五郎にコナンもついて行くが、待ち合わせ場所に向かっていた途中、突然響き渡った銃声—。  果たせなかった約束と、隻眼に宿った残像。氷雪吹き荒れる山岳で、白き闇の因縁（ホワイトアウトミステリー）の幕が切って落とされる―"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Conan: One-Eyed Flashback","runtime":109,"tagline":"The once sleeping case is now awake ⎯","homepage":"","overview":"As police inspector Yamato Kansuke pursues a certain man in the snowy mountains of Nagano, a shadow suddenly appears in his field of vision. While he's distracted, a rifle bullet fired by someone grazes his left eye and causes an avalanche accompanied by a roar. Ten months later, Kansuke, having miraculously survived the avalanche, receives a report that a researcher at the Nobeyama National Astronomical Observatory has been attacked."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Thám Tử Lừng Danh Conan: Dư Ảnh Của Độc Nhãn","runtime":0,"tagline":"Tôi đã nhớ ra nó.","homepage":"https://moveek.com/phim/conan-movie-28/","overview":"Thám Tử Lừng Danh Conan 28: Dư Ảnh Của Độc Nhãn – Trên những ngọn núi tuyết của Nagano, một vụ án bí ẩn đã đưa Conan và các thám tử quay trở lại quá khứ. Thanh tra Yamato Kansuke - người đã bị thương nặng trong một trận tuyết lở nhiều năm trước - bất ngờ phải đối mặt với những ký ức đau thương của mình trong khi điều tra một vụ tấn công tại Đài quan sát Nobeyama. Cùng lúc đó, Mori Kogoro nhận được một cuộc gọi từ một đồng nghiệp cũ, tiết lộ mối liên hệ đáng ngờ giữa anh ta và vụ án đã bị lãng quên từ lâu. Sự xuất hiện của Morofushi Takaaki, cùng với những nhân vật chủ chốt như Amuro Tooru, Kazami và cảnh sát Tokyo, càng làm phức tạp thêm cuộc điều tra. Khi quá khứ và hiện tại đan xen, một bí ẩn rùng rợn dần dần được hé lộ - và ký ức của Kansuke nắm giữ chìa khóa cho mọi thứ."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"명탐정 코난: 척안의 잔상","runtime":110,"tagline":"기억이 돌아왔다...","homepage":"","overview":"국립천문대 노베야마의 괴한 침입 사건을 조사하던 나가노현경 형사 야마토 칸스케. 사건을 수사하던 중, 천문대의 파라볼라 안테나가 움직이자 10개월 전 눈사태 속 총격 피습으로 인한 왼쪽 눈의 상처에 갑자기 통증이 이는데… 그날 밤, 모리 코고로에게 형사 시절의 옛 동료 와니 형사의 전화가 걸려 온다. 나가노현 눈사태 사고의 내막을 조사하고 있던 와니는 사건 파일에서 모리 탐정의 이름을 발견, 참고 차 모리 탐정과 만나기로 한다. 약속 당일, 코난과 란도 모리 탐정을 따라 약속 장소로 향하지만 그곳에서 의문의 총성이 울려 퍼진다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Détective Conan : La Mémoire retrouvée","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"À Tokyo, Conan assiste impuissant à l’assassinat d’un ancien collègue de Kogorô. Déterminé à venger son ami en débusquant le meurtrier, ce dernier remonte une piste qui le conduit aux montagnes enneigées de Nagano. Sur place, il fera équipe avec Kansuke Yamato qui a lui-même été gravement blessé lors d’une avalanche 10 mois plus tôt. Or ses souvenirs perdus pourraient bien fournir la clef pour résoudre l’enquête."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"El caso que una vez estuvo dormido ahora está despierto.","homepage":"","overview":"Mientras el inspector de policía Yamato Kansuke persigue a un hombre en las montañas nevadas de Nagano, una sombra aparece repentinamente en su campo de visión. Mientras está distraído, una bala de fusil disparada por alguien le roza el ojo izquierdo y provoca una avalancha acompañada de un rugido. Diez meses después, Kansuke, tras sobrevivir milagrosamente a la avalancha, recibe un informe de que un investigador del Observatorio Astronómico Nacional de Nobeyama ha sido atacado."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"El detectiu Conan: One-eyed flashback","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mentre l'inspector de policia Yamato Kansuke persegueix un home a les muntanyes nevades de Nagano, de sobte apareix una ombra al seu camp de visió. Mentre està distret, una bala de rifle disparada per algú li rasca l'ull esquerre i provoca una allau acompanyada d'un rugit. Deu mesos després, en Kansuke, després d'haver sobreviscut miraculosament a l'allau, rep un avís alertant que un investigador de l'Observatori Astronòmic Nacional de Nobeyama ha estat atacat."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"名偵探柯南：獨眼的殘像","runtime":0,"tagline":"那沉睡多時的記憶，突然甦醒——","homepage":"","overview":"長野縣警大和敢助在八岳連峰未寶岳的雪山中追捕某名「男子」之際，遭到男子襲擊並遭到雪崩埋沒。10 個月之後，國立天文台野邊山的研究員因為不明原因遭受攻擊，在雪崩中奇蹟生還的敢助，與上原由衣前往了現場。  讓人意想不到的是，來到現場的敢助，隨著天文台的大型天線啟動，受傷的左眼竟突開始感受到劇痛？另一邊，毛利小五郎與過去在警視廳時期的好友，為了調查 10 個月前的雪崩事件準備會合，沒想到前往途中卻突然傳出槍響！一場覆蓋在暴雪下的神祕事件就此揭開序幕。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"ยอดนักสืบจิ๋วโคนัน เดอะมูฟวี่ 28: ปริศนาภาพติดตามรณะ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"สารวัตรยามาโตะ คันซึเกะ แห่งกรมตำรวจจังหวัดนากาโนะ ได้รับบาดเจ็บที่ตาซ้ายจากกระสุนไรเฟิลของชายปริศนาระหว่างการไล่ล่าบนภูเขาหิมะ ทำให้เขาสูญเสียการมองเห็นที่ตาข้างนั้นไป สิบเดือนต่อมา ขณะสอบสวนเหตุการณ์ใหม่ อุเอฮาระ ยูอิ ได้พบกับยามาโตะซึ่งยังมีชีวิตอยู่ และด้วยเหตุผลบางอย่าง ยามาโตะก็รู้สึกปวดตาซ้ายอย่างรุนแรง ขณะเดียวกัน โมริ โคโกโร่ ได้รับโทรศัพท์จากอดีตเพื่อนร่วมงานเกี่ยวกับคดีหิมะถล่มที่ยามาโตะเคยเกี่ยวข้อง ทั้งโคโกโร่ และโคนัน จึงไปยังสถานที่นัดหมาย ทันใดนั้นเองเสียงปืนปริศนาก็เกิดดังขึ้น! เรื่องราวปริศนาที่เกิดขึ้นบนภูเขาหิมะในจังหวัดนากาโนะกำลังจะเริ่มต้นขึ้นแล้ว!"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"名偵探柯南：獨眼的殘像","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"長野縣．八嶽聯峰未寶嶽。長野縣警大和敢助在雪山追捕「某名男子」時，一抹身影突然映入他的眼簾。在他分心的瞬間，「某名男子」擊出的步槍子彈擦過敢助的左眼，地面轟然雷動，雪崩隨之發生，直接將敢助吞沒—— 10 個月後。國立天文台野邊山所屬設施的研究人員遭到不明人士襲擊，接獲通報後，從雪崩中奇蹟生還的敢助與上原由衣立即趕往現場。在他們進行調查途中，天文台的巨型鑊形天線啟動時，因負傷而變成獨眼的敢助，左眼突然無故劇烈地疼痛起來…… 當天晚上，毛利偵探事務所接到了小五郎任職警視廳時交情好的同事，被稱為「鱷魚」的刑警來電。他表示自己正在調查波及敢助的未寶嶽雪崩事故，並在案件資料中發現小五郎的名字。小五郎跟他相約幾天后會面，柯南也跟著小五郎赴約，不料前往約定地點途中卻突然傳來巨大的槍聲——。\r 在冰雪紛飛的山嶽上，白茫茫的宿命即將揭開序幕——"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Als politie-inspecteur Yamato Kansuke een bepaalde man achtervolgt in de besneeuwde bergen van Nagano, verschijnt er plotseling een schaduw in zijn gezichtsveld. Terwijl hij afgeleid is, schampt een geweerkogel die door iemand wordt afgevuurd zijn linkeroog en veroorzaakt een lawine die gepaard gaat met een gebrul.  Tien maanden later ontvangt Kansuke, die op wonderbaarlijke wijze de lawine heeft overleefd, een bericht dat een onderzoeker van het Nobeyama National Astronomical Observatory is aangevallen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"المحقق كونان: فلاش باك ذو العين الواحدة","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Детектив Конан: Воспоминания одноглазого","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Во время преследования в заснеженных горах Нагано инспектор Ямато Канскэ отвлекается на внезапно появившуюся тень. В этот момент пуля неизвестного ранит его в левый глаз, а выстрел вызывает сход лавины. Спустя десять месяцев чудом выживший Канскэ получает отчёт о нападении на исследователя из Национальной Астрономической Обсерватории Нобэяма."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Detektiv Conan Film 28: Der Flashback des Einäugigen","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Yamato und Yui Uehara von der Polizei Nagano werden alarmiert, dass ein Forscher von einer vermummten Gestalt in einem Observatorium in den Yatsugatake-Bergen angegriffen wurde. Während der Ermittlungen verspürt Kansuke plötzlich ein seltsames Ziehen in dem Auge, das er sich vor zehn Monaten bei einer Lawine verletzt hatte.Zur selben Zeit wird Kogorô von seinem früheren Kollegen Sametani kontaktiert. Der behauptet, eine heiße Spur im Zusammenhang mit Kansukes Lawinenunfall zu haben. Doch bevor sie sich treffen können, wird Sametani direkt vor Kogorô und Conan eiskalt erschossen. Um der Sache nachzugehen, reist Kogorô nach Nagano, während Conan gemeinsam mit Amuro und Kazami zu ermitteln beginnt. Vor Ort stoßen sie bei ihren Ermittlungen auf einen Raubüberfall, der sich vor acht Jahren ereignet hat. Doch als plötzlich jemand gezielt Kansuke nach dem Leben trachtet, stellt sich die Frage: Kann Conan die Angriffe stoppen und die Wahrheit ans Licht bringen?"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Dedektif Conan: Tek Gözlü Geriye Dönüş","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Polis müfettişi Yamato Kansuke, Nagano'nun karlı dağlarında bir adamın peşindeyken, görüş alanında aniden bir gölge belirir. Dikkatinin dağıldığı o anda, kimliği belirsiz birinin ateşlediği tüfek mermisi sol gözünü sıyırır ve büyük bir gürültüyle birlikte çığ düşmesine neden olur. On ay sonra, çığdan mucizevi bir şekilde kurtulan Kansuke, Nobeyama Ulusal Astronomi Gözlemevi'nde bir araştırmacının saldırıya uğradığına dair bir ihbar alır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"68e934ac85dc7322deaa1ced","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68e934ac85dc7322deaa1ced","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-10-10T16:30:36.678Z","updated_at":"2025-10-10T16:33:55.297Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":6,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":257512,"adult":false,"title":"Detective Conan: Dimensional Sniper","video":false,"overview":"A rash of sniper attacks leaves the streets of Tokyo empty and the public terrified to go outside. It’s up to Conan and his friends to find the culprit, but the case goes deeper than it seems. Military cover-ups, conspiracies and murder abound in this fast-paced, thrilling mystery!","genre_ids":[16,28,18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1183,"vote_count":130,"poster_path":"/d08RKnmdcoCwlHOezazli8hmJH6.jpg","release_date":"2014-04-19","vote_average":6.831,"backdrop_path":"/5ucjKx2rR8Z55Qd7lK5mBtQPGkr.jpg","original_title":"名探偵コナン 異次元の狙撃手","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1304434,"adult":false,"title":"Nobody","video":false,"overview":"The Little Pig Yao decides to leave Langlang Mountain to join the pilgrimage. On the journey west, what trials will the little monsters face? In the end, will they achieve their dreams and live as they truly desire?","genre_ids":[16,12,14,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.961,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/oqS3wJX3wNj4DciCyTznnMZ3Fuu.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-02","vote_average":7.805,"backdrop_path":"/xawDFjfjBmtKYC29bZOYnYPGa8e.jpg","original_title":"浪浪山小妖怪","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1137179,"adult":false,"title":"Yadang: The Snitch","video":false,"overview":"Navigating both the criminal underworld and law enforcement agencies, professional snitches called \"yadang\" provide covert information about the drug world to prosecutors and police. When a drug bust at a party attended by high-profile second-generation VIPs entangles those involved into a dangerous conspiracy, a seasoned yadang must do everything in his power not just to make it out on top, but alive.","genre_ids":[80,28,35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.7358,"vote_count":36,"poster_path":"/y7dsDbG8zVWkrkyOhA6ckZXX1uC.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-16","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/9pdoEzieGdUTlRWTAO7QP8q1tIo.jpg","original_title":"야당","original_language":"ko"},{"id":12521,"adult":false,"title":"Shocker","video":false,"overview":"About to be electrocuted for a catalog of heinous crimes, the unrepentant Horace Pinker transforms into a terrifying energy source. Only young athlete Jonathan Parker, with an uncanny connection to him through bizarre dreams, can fight the powerful demon.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3774,"vote_count":455,"poster_path":"/m5EKmXhFFq8wg6xE15eEoKaHfnO.jpg","release_date":"1989-03-23","vote_average":5.56,"backdrop_path":"/1F5OOV5gipfGbfSJgQdV29xlNi.jpg","original_title":"Shocker","original_language":"en"},{"id":27799,"adult":false,"title":"Hana & Alice","video":false,"overview":"Two teenage best pals attracted to the same boy end up scrambling his life after he walks into a door and is knocked unconscious.","genre_ids":[18,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2592,"vote_count":129,"poster_path":"/bkEn15Jm8Edl40ra0qRJny2MYTq.jpg","release_date":"2004-03-13","vote_average":6.938,"backdrop_path":"/mSPCNxQ6qqF4uawIqBxfhqwslxI.jpg","original_title":"花とアリス","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1426616,"adult":false,"title":"WWE Clash in Paris 2025","video":true,"overview":"WWE Clash in Paris was a professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) and live-streaming event produced by the American company World Wrestling Entertainment (WWE). It took place on Sunday, August 31, 2025, at the Paris La Défense Arena in La Défense, Nanterre, France.","genre_ids":[28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2981,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/sbEL4nHZ2Ze9Js3Oa5Sv1Mpqqu2.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-31","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/su5uD5wCE3E4glgwe0mEU9UQuzN.jpg","original_title":"WWE Clash in Paris 2025","original_language":"en"},{"id":1490213,"adult":false,"title":"Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Entertainment District Decisive Battle Arc","video":false,"overview":"After facing many dangers in the brothel town, Tanjiro, Zenitsu and Inosuke, along with the Flame Pillar Tengen Uzui, enter a deadly battle with the Upper Moon Six pair – Daki and Gyutaro. The fierce confrontation not only shows the strength of teamwork but also highlights the spirit of sacrifice of the Pillars. This is one of the most epic and emotional battles in the entire series.","genre_ids":[16,28,14,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5602,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/mXIb8ftj5WlJUWvtJteFgLIZxke.jpg","release_date":"2023-03-01","vote_average":9.2,"backdrop_path":"/gtQaq8HNSJByLXqs8vwDHabnP4p.jpg","original_title":"鬼滅の刃 遊郭決戦編","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1450981,"adult":false,"title":"It Takes More Than a Pretty Face to Fall in Love","video":false,"overview":"Sana, obsessed with boys with handsome faces, suddenly encounters her idol, Kanato. He has been skipping school and is on the verge of being expelled, and he has a request for Sana.","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4429,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/yLhwVydaUhh0qcfPpEA3HC2wnD1.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-14","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/3t8OWaxmhdVmXKWG0MTBUzVV2aY.jpg","original_title":"顔だけじゃ好きになりません","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1276073,"adult":false,"title":"Bullet Train Explosion","video":false,"overview":"When panic erupts on a Tokyo-bound bullet train that will explode if it slows below 100 kph, authorities race against time to save everyone on board.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7233,"vote_count":292,"poster_path":"/jmzxlDBwgvRbpPJzNQwizyn9UEn.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-23","vote_average":6.851,"backdrop_path":"/zHP9pMtYuMZBluNZNBP9i5fX2US.jpg","original_title":"新幹線大爆破","original_language":"ja"},{"id":980477,"adult":false,"title":"Ne Zha 2","video":false,"overview":"After a catastrophic event leaves their bodies destroyed, Ne Zha and Ao Bing are granted a fragile second chance at life. As tensions rise between the dragon clans and celestial forces, the two must undergo a series of perilous trials that will test their bond, challenge their identities, and decide the fate of both mortals and immortals.","genre_ids":[16,14,12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.7072,"vote_count":594,"poster_path":"/cb5NyNrqiCNNoDkA8FfxHAtypdG.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-29","vote_average":8.11,"backdrop_path":"/8btfz81bOJ2lC7cujYBTw03wzg3.jpg","original_title":"哪吒之魔童闹海","original_language":"zh"},{"id":744653,"adult":false,"title":"The Thursday Murder Club","video":false,"overview":"A group of senior sleuths passionate about solving cold cases get plunged into a real-life murder mystery in this comic crime caper.","genre_ids":[35,9648,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.2085,"vote_count":908,"poster_path":"/jbnazCHr8S2l2glyvjPTpa4NbEw.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-22","vote_average":6.599,"backdrop_path":"/4KN06gns94rQFoYQWDGunK7Cob4.jpg","original_title":"The Thursday Murder Club","original_language":"en"},{"id":1242011,"adult":false,"title":"Together","video":false,"overview":"Years into their relationship, Tim and Millie find themselves at a crossroads as they move to the country, abandoning all that is familiar in their lives except each other. With tensions already flaring, a nightmarish encounter with a mysterious, unnatural force threatens to