y, love, and the choices that make a life.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.6651,"vote_count":2205,"poster_path":"/k3waqVXSnvCZWfJYNtdamTgTtTA.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-02","vote_average":7.719,"backdrop_path":"/7HR38hMBl23lf38MAN63y4pKsHz.jpg","original_title":"Past Lives","original_language":"en"},{"id":1084199,"adult":false,"title":"Companion","video":false,"overview":"During a weekend getaway at a secluded lakeside estate, a group of friends finds themselves entangled in a web of secrets, deception, and advanced technology. As tensions rise and loyalties are tested, they uncover unsettling truths about themselves and the world around them.","genre_ids":[27,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.4777,"vote_count":2099,"poster_path":"/oCoTgC3UyWGfyQ9thE10ulWR7bn.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-22","vote_average":7.012,"backdrop_path":"/qA6MHDGDY0LyutjLUgFJRbPXLpW.jpg","original_title":"Companion","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":1058521,"adult":false,"title":"Still Life","video":false,"overview":"A detective slowly unravels as a serial killer taunts him with depictions of his gruesome crimes.","genre_ids":[27,9648,80],"popularity":0.1388,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/adV0Jnlq4A9obQ4ogubuG3k3cdv.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Still Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":462677,"adult":false,"title":"Doraemon: Nobita's Great Adventure in the Antarctic Kachi Kochi","video":false,"overview":"Doraemon and Nobita discover a mysterious golden ring far beneath the ice in Antarctica, leading them to uncover an ancient, ruined city.","genre_ids":[16,12,14,10751],"popularity":1.617,"vote_count":101,"poster_path":"/hcydn0Lr3DAixZFOaUmjoqoIFU6.jpg","release_date":"2017-03-04","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/3W2I33pTXWMiH8py382Zg86OB9Q.jpg","original_title":"映画ドラえもん のび太の南極カチコチ大冒険","original_language":"ja"},{"id":3132,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Company","video":false,"overview":"When a Harvard-educated CIA agent is killed during an operation, the secret agency recruits his twin brother.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,53],"popularity":2.6096,"vote_count":845,"poster_path":"/umu141mcfIEhRLgyQp7TWlGJFW.jpg","release_date":"2002-06-07","vote_average":5.513,"backdrop_path":"/9oLrsekWm3sfEGw5HOav6roW1h7.jpg","original_title":"Bad Company","original_language":"en"},{"id":3049,"adult":false,"title":"Ace Ventura: Pet Detective","video":false,"overview":"He's Ace Ventura: Pet Detective. The Ace is on the case to find the Miami Dolphins' missing mascot and quarterback Dan Marino. He goes eyeball to eyeball with a man-eating shark, stakes out the Miami Dolphins and woos and wows the ladies. Whether he's undercover, under fire or underwater, he always gets his man… or beast!","genre_ids":[35,9648,80],"popularity":5.4349,"vote_count":6235,"poster_path":"/pqiRuETmuSybfnVZ7qyeoXhQyN1.jpg","release_date":"1994-02-04","vote_average":6.572,"backdrop_path":"/nbvREKIjX16mwNZtFqAoQTTHPnQ.jpg","original_title":"Ace Ventura: Pet Detective","original_language":"en"},{"id":1063161,"adult":false,"title":"1888","video":false,"overview":"When Demonetization (currency ban) is announced in India, 3 unlikely characters come face to face for a bag of cash. After that a car journey begins and some more characters come into picture. This results in a cat and mouse game with a very unexpected outcome.","genre_ids":[53,80,28,18],"popularity":0.1746,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/sY4f3X5yvyI6XLKpocCEr5XBdPQ.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-09","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/37wFKdoXdTC89md5FWmCNbVAFHh.jpg","original_title":"1888","original_language":"kn"},{"id":1062807,"adult":false,"title":"SPY x FAMILY CODE: White","video":false,"overview":"While under the guise of taking his family on a weekend winter getaway, Loid's attempt to make progress on his current mission Operation Strix proves difficult when Anya mistakenly gets involved and triggers events that threaten world peace.","genre_ids":[16,35,12,28],"popularity":5.0115,"vote_count":610,"poster_path":"/xlIQf4y9eB14iYzNN142tROIWON.jpg","release_date":"2023-12-22","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/zVDJ4cRgSpHlILSm7kGiklHQ6O7.jpg","original_title":"劇場版 SPY×FAMILY CODE: White","original_language":"ja"},{"id":467260,"adult":false,"title":"Chinpira","video":false,"overview":"Osamu rescues a girl who was being chased by two punks and is soon mixed up with the Yakuza","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":0.2639,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/oeMvhGzDFtEqe5MhLxQ3A4Dkohc.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-11","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/kjhGSa0izGAHkmih0niU6uc5jSq.jpg","original_title":"弱虫　チンピラ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":857862,"adult":false,"title":"EVANGELION: DEATH (TRUE)²","video":false,"overview":"A highly experimental film presenting a story out of chronological order taking place 15 years after a near-apocalyptic catastrophe, about four traumatized 14 year olds who are tasked with piloting massive humanoid decisive weapons called Evangelion, the psychologically maladjusted adults who handle and command them, and the events and forces that affect them or which they take part in as they engage massive hostile invaders known as \"Angels.\"","genre_ids":[16,878,28,18],"popularity":2.1988,"vote_count":115,"poster_path":"/AehyZFGm68ep76b81IbLJ1EJ5ot.jpg","release_date":"1998-03-07","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/fZxQc2xBqxOJt6q0R8bwq5oe7C9.jpg","original_title":"EVANGELION:DEATH(TRUE)²","original_language":"ja"},{"id":467169,"adult":false,"title":"Eureka Seven Hi-Evolution 1","video":false,"overview":"It all begins with the story that was left untold—the earth-shattering incident where Renton's father disappeared. With the mysterious pilot Eureka by his side, only Adroc Thurston could undo his own mistake, sparking the event that changed everything and earned him the title of a hero. Now, ten years later, Eureka lies in critical condition as Renton leaves the crew of the Gekko. But when he finds himself in the care of his father's old friends, he has a choice to make. Either stay with the loving family he's always wanted, or earn the love he seeks.","genre_ids":[18,16,878,12,28],"popularity":1.0324,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/ivfU7kNHkdX7VPSoeVljbkQ2xvm.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-16","vote_average":4.875,"backdrop_path":"/pY6Cq1aXXLSAdcfR6pXMRIBbQGV.jpg","original_title":"交響詩篇エウレカセブン ハイエボリューション1","original_language":"ja"},{"id":467170,"adult":false,"title":"Dance with Devils: Fortuna","video":false,"overview":"Ritsuka Tachibana. She lives a calm and unchanging life. Ritsuka's older brother Lindo returns from studying abroad in the United Kingdom. Shikou Academy student council president Rem Kaginuki calls on the girl, and she begins having mysterious encounters with the student council members. Her life changed a little from that day, but Ritsuka expected nothing more.  However, she comes home to find her mother collapsed with suspicious hooded men nearby. They were not human but devils, vampires, and exorcists seeking the Forbidden Grimoire. Ritsuka's former daily life crumbles around her, and she finds herself slowly becoming attracted to Rem, who helps her in her predicament. On the other hand, confusion deepens with regard to her brother who carries a secret. Ritsuka is unsure what path to choose as she finds herself at the center of a love story.  (Source: ANN)","genre_ids":[16,14,10749],"popularity":0.3538,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/bhnYrvDHt4AhxCqo2FOdcVyPV6O.jpg","release_date":"2017-11-04","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Dance with Devils -Fortuna-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":467172,"adult":false,"title":"DC Super Heroes vs. Eagle Talon","video":false,"overview":"Joker has come to Japan to steal the Eagle Talon Society's secret weapons in his continued scheme for pure chaos. However, the Justice League is on his trail, but there's something off with Batman. Now, it's up to Eagle Talon to go find out what's wrong with Batman, and that means going back in time to Bruce Wayne's most traumatic experience, the murder of his parents. If that wasn't enough to worry about, the Eagle Talon Society also have to keep their eyes on their production budget, especially with most of that money going towards the licensing fee for DC's popular characters. Will the Eagle Talon Society and the Justice League be able to stop the Joker before their budget dries up, and they're reduced to simple stick figures!?","genre_ids":[28,16,35],"popularity":0.3714,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/wTnuhMGXWprk2syHLtBBi2ZndIh.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-21","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/aY8vmigBHaOVLhvRb0UFfATcuTV.jpg","original_title":"DCスーパーヒーローズvs鷹の爪団","original_language":"ja"},{"id":469912,"adult":false,"title":"Donten: Laughing Under the Clouds - Gaiden: Chapter 1 - One Year After the Battle","video":false,"overview":"One year has passed after the great battle against the Orochi (gigantic snake). Tenka Kumo had been paralyzed from the final battle and he took part of the government’s human experiment before the battle. Tenka withdrew himself from society but his younger brothers Soramaru and Chutaro find out the secret past about their older brother.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,14],"popularity":0.7991,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/8eHhIEsSXMZ5Q502B4cKgdmEgOK.jpg","release_date":"2017-12-02","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/bze1JwHhnqK6NzsytbZsgZoo88J.jpg","original_title":"曇天に笑う＜外伝＞～決別、犲の誓い～","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1458643,"adult":false,"title":"Twins Hinahima","video":false,"overview":"Two girls dream of going viral on TikTok until they discover something strange in their videos.","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.2085,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/jZjjExtPubcdteOQTSIS0j5eKdV.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-28","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/gMWCBtvIWLm4APa2qlF7QATvQS3.jpg","original_title":"ツインズひなひま","original_language":"ja"},{"id":6973,"adult":false,"title":"In the Valley of Elah","video":false,"overview":"A career officer and his wife work with a police detective to uncover the truth behind their son's disappearance following his return from a tour of duty in Iraq.","genre_ids":[36,18,53,80,9648],"popularity":1.465,"vote_count":1067,"poster_path":"/ufCkeypovY01Dm123I2aPvGUA5H.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-14","vote_average":6.795,"backdrop_path":"/2etSwBHCTcyFp9XOjZR4yYxqCC9.jpg","original_title":"In the Valley of Elah","original_language":"en"},{"id":7007,"adult":false,"title":"Rising Sun","video":false,"overview":"When a prostitute is found dead in a Los Angeles skyscraper occupied by a large Japanese corporation, detectives John Connor and Web Smith are called in to investigate. Although Connor has previous experience working in Japan, cultural differences make their progress difficult until a security disc showing the murder turns up. Close scrutiny proves the disc has been doctored, and the detectives realize they're dealing with a cover-up as well.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"popularity":1.4943,"vote_count":817,"poster_path":"/jVWEeZ383peKxwE284AdyHqq6GH.jpg","release_date":"1993-07-30","vote_average":6.138,"backdrop_path":"/dmaLmrP3PYfhb8P2SWMucZCZqjk.jpg","original_title":"Rising Sun","original_language":"en"},{"id":1458730,"adult":false,"title":"To Live and Die Under a Shadow","video":false,"overview":"Paralyzed by post-grad anxiety, a burned-out Jake spends his last summer beneath Boulder, Colorado's Flatirons. When a mysterious discovery threatens to consume him entirely and plunges him into a surreal nightmare.","genre_ids":[9648,53],"popularity":0.1354,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/16C3ewrvKEI39kOw3MLkS6wdQ0f.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"To Live and Die Under a Shadow","original_language":"en"},{"id":7304,"adult":false,"title":"Running Scared","video":false,"overview":"A low-ranking thug is entrusted by his boss to dispose of a gun that killed corrupt cops, but things spiral out of control when the gun ends up in wrong hands.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":1.4544,"vote_count":1119,"poster_path":"/wVlwZbwJlI5C33STslTyVNRGjg6.jpg","release_date":"2006-01-06","vote_average":6.985,"backdrop_path":"/p5z5X3GRnaFEqgtEa7fiGhgtUkA.jpg","original_title":"Running Scared","original_language":"en"},{"id":1059572,"adult":false,"title":"New Dimension! Crayon Shin-chan the Movie: Battle of Supernatural Powers ~Flying Sushi~","video":false,"overview":"40-years ago, there was a prophecy claiming that in the year of “20” and “23”, two emitting lights would come to the Earth from outer space. And the dark light with strong power will bring out a huge disaster. In the summer of 2023, as predicted, two mysterious lights approach Japan and descend on Kasukabe. The white light hits Shin-chan, which makes him get a superpower. Meanwhile, a man called Mitsuru Hiriya, has been bathed in dark light and has acquired psychic powers begins to run amok. A man who wants the destruction of the world, Hiriya VS A happy-go-lucky kindergarten child, Shinnosuke. A superpower battle is going to begin!","genre_ids":[16,35,28,12,10751,14,878],"popularity":1.4828,"vote_count":40,"poster_path":"/a56Fm2YWrlnqlC3TIgDvCJdzlKI.jpg","release_date":"2023-08-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/gjEiHrj8dSsgL25XbIxT9o5qO3u.jpg","original_title":"しん次元！クレヨンしんちゃんTHE MOVIE 超能力大決戦 ～とべとべ手巻き寿司～","original_language":"ja"},{"id":271948,"adult":false,"title":"STAR DRIVER: The Movie","video":false,"overview":"Star Driver takes place on the fictional Southern Cross Isle. One night, a boy named Takuto washes up on shore swimming from the mainland. He later enrolls in Southern Cross High School as a freshman and makes new friends.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,10749,18,878],"popularity":0.7323,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/i5jdOxUrVxVH24WSV1UbypBjfnv.jpg","release_date":"2013-02-09","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/jCEM9uoMRmz73iNcubAhpWIuH7l.jpg","original_title":"スタードライ